{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if we had the means to survive, we survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they were not prepared to feed us; and to bring all the money we had, and all the jewelry we had, in case we had-- we can-- they never thought we-- we had so much; and to come forward.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise, if you don't compile with their-- comply their with their-- their-- their-- you know, their asking, they will shot the men that they were already there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, which woman will go and leave behind-- you know-- will hide and leave their husband, their sons, or their brothers in the powers of the Germans?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all went, voluntarily.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as I was saying, everybody is-- you know, buried their-- their treasure in their house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That same day, my mother send me to Rhodes Island, in the Juderia, though it was very, very dangerous to go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew exactly where all our things were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- it-- it was not difficult to-- it was a plank under the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, we had lots of jewelry there hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beside all this from my mother, we had two old aunties who lived with us at the moment of the concentration camp, you know-- at the time of taking us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Their children were some in South America, some in North America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were staying with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they giving, you know, for safekeeping, all the jewelry to my father, because he was their nephew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, the war was going to finish-- to send them to their children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went myself, and I took a bag, a very big bag, and I put it all my jewelry of my family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went back that night to-- to Kremasto, where we were staying.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
